OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine into
OL,6,Fthe evening, with some late sunshine
OL,7,Fgiving way to overnight clear periods.
OL,8,FWinds gradually easing, with a slight
OL,9,Ffrost developing in some rural areas.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA fine start, feeling warm
OL,12,Fwith some sunshine. Cloudier
OL,13,Fconditions and some rain or showers
OL,14,Fwill make gradual inroads from the
OL,15,Fwest later, perhaps culminating in
OL,16,Fsome thundery showers locally.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
